OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fduring strike over pay     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Thousands of teachers have joined      
OL,6, rallies in Scottish cities as part of  
OL,7, the country's first national schools   
OL,8, strike since the 1980s.                
OL,10,FIt has led to the closure of nearly    
OL,11,Fevery primary and secondary school in  
OL,12,Fthe country, and many council          
OL,13,Fnurseries.                             
OL,15,FA revised pay offer put to unions on   
OL,16,FTuesday was rejected as "insulting".   
OL,18,FBut Education Secretary Shirley-Anne   
OL,19,FSomerville said their demands for a 10%
OL,20,Fpay rise were "unaffordable".          
